Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.05,0:00:07.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是否还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.71,0:00:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  为了还清总额一亿五千万的债务
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也为了保护凪大小姐而战斗着的管家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫崎飒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这种无所谓的事情就暂且丢在一边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.28,0:00:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回就让我们尽情地无视原作和时间空间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夏天的沙滩举行泳装大会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀必死杀必死…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀必死杀必死…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀必死杀必死…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:39.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（EVA预告中三石每次都会说的台词）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热天很夏  泳装篇！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:50.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（此处标题刻意改变了语序：正确的语序为ナツがアツいぜ(夏天很热)）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:54.50,jinggao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}翻译：一；校对：无爱的飞鱼、遠ぃ風；时间：黑羽侖人；后期：zipwinmax。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  真气派
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.66,0:00:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像在南方的小岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.19,0:01:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这宅邸里面  居然还有这样的私人沙滩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  还有这么完美的游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这里是练马区  实在让人难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.23,0:01:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.25,0:01:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这没什么大不了的  总共才花了几百亿而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.36,0:01:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那边的椰子树每十棵也就才值一亿五千万而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一亿五千万？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就和我欠的钱一样多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种破地方究竟有什么好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是老爷子自己的特殊嗜好而建起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.16,0:01:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  难得有这样的沙滩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.81,0:01:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没理由不游一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒  人在水里是浮不起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒  小凪是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来大小姐是旱鸭子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！人本来就是陆生动物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以人的身体构造是不可能在水中生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:02:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来教您游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试看吧  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个嘛…既然小飒都说到这份上了就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就赶快换上泳衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳…泳衣？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等…等等  难道是要我穿泳衣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…泳衣的话  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说还太早了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.29,0:02:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总…总之  我是绝对不会去游泳的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了  就凭那种水中专用型还想赢主角机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:33.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（众多的Gundam主角们都削过水中专用型的人棍…最近的貌似就是刹那了…）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人以泳装相对 这也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  小凪这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐生这么大的气…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是哪里又做错了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒  接下来就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近可好啊  小凪  哈亚太君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是来玩的～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是被硬拉来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  听说小凪愿意「免费」请我们去游泳池玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把大家叫来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不记得有说过那种话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不是很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.47,0:03:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经为大家准备好各种泳衣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请选一件自己喜欢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大的沙滩  不用的话也是浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凪  不介意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我是绝对不会去游泳的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:03:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉亚小姐  这样真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然交给桂老师去做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  正如老师所说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起游得很高兴的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凪也会想一起游的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果真是那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  小飒也选一件怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得非常适合你呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉亚小姐  别耍我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还真意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个桂老师居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我之前误解她了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你会遵守约定的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  在这里喝酒喝到爽是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您尽情喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  大家今天尽情地喝…呃不对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽情地游泳吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉让大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌Show  大家已经准备好了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在  Let's  go！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等  从刚才开始就在拍些什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我觉得刚才的镜头很有记录的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  对我们动画研究部来说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是不可错过的镜头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:06:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这泳衣  感觉布料相当少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主  听好了  绝对不可以看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀  亘  脸怎么那么红呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我哪有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  脚踏两船呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  你个色小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  喜欢哪个多点？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那当然是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主…下流！无耻！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亘 你果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:43.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不是的  不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  果然什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  亘真H！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲夜你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…你们两个误会我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…那个…只是被咲夜问到哪个比较喜欢  然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说  大家都玩得很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞这种大贱卖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低级的卖肉往往会意外导致人气的急剧下降哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  不过我觉得这样很健康啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道不  牧村老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样与学生小鬼们交流  也是咱当老师的很重要的工作之一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白不？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  受教了  前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为替上帝引导这些孩子们的指路人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也十分赞同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你理解咱说的话了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  满上  满上～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过是个路过的修女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:57.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（假面骑士DECADE：我只不过是个路过的假面骑士）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～虽说也有若干例外啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐也去和大家一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊  那只不过是小鬼级别的玩法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起跟他们一起胡闹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看某动画公司的股票狂跌的样子要有趣多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:17.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（GONZO公司股票已于090401被摘牌）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  其实还是很在意的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书都拿反了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨蛋  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  这是故意的…故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做大脑体操
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ta…Tareraya…Renoo…Oogu…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兴趣的话 小飒也一起来游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…不过把大小姐一个人丢在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没关系的  你们两个想去的话就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人也能自娱自乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接下来准备把「豹头战士的冒险绘卷」一天内看完
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一天之内吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒这个笨蛋  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不理解我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才似乎感觉到有一股邪气…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时  在豪宅门口站着的某位少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那个被硬拽上巨大机器人的少年一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦恼着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:41.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（大家都听出来是吐嘈「碇真嗣」了吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  姐姐又给大家添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏？我现在在小凪家里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家玩得很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  在姐姐继续添麻烦之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把她带走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  我这是第一次来小飒住的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我是在紧张什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过是来接走姐姐的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是啊  又不是特意跑来见小飒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可以打扰一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个是在商店街抽奖抽中的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂流河免费入场卷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和我一起被冲走…好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:51.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（雕像捏自1970年大阪世博会雕像「太阳塔」）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样  小飒会答应一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏菊小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是哈亚太君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我们为对手  居然还能一直赢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然仅靠泉一个人是无法与之抗衡的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  你们两个也给我认真点打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:27.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好接着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒你这叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白野威
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  你是来安慰我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世态炎凉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭哟  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐你不是还有我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你们都打算背叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有我的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…无视我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戏份到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要过去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意小凪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是大小姐还真是固执啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子也差不多该屈服了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐  怎么样了？差不多该…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑到哪里去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱歌小姐  千樱小姐  对…对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  这还真是意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫崎君居然是个变态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就说我是变态…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  我完全不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  一点都不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:30.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Japnica弱点薄：捏自Fate/hollow ataraxia中的「ジャプニカ暗殺帳」\N实为影射「ジャポニカ学習帳」——日本一系列专为小学生而设的笔记用本）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子已经下狠心了  明明超在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总…总之  对不起了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳  没想到居然在那种地方换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…飒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏…雏菊小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那个  我其实不想看的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:13:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想看…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:02.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…小飒  那是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在说我的裸体没有一点看的价值吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  又要被雏菊小姐讨厌了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.61,0:14:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  原本是想和小飒拉近距离的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但又对他发脾气了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这泳衣是不是太大胆了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  连这种程度都做不到的话怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少能引起小飒的注意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西泽同学比想象中要成熟得多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天起可以叫你「Honey」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那样的话  我也可以叫小飒作…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…西泽同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小飒…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在必须快点找到大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐  总算找到您了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒你非要一起游泳  我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  小飒  刚才那是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…能不能当作没发生过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的事就当作没发生过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都请不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒你这花心大萝卜！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙希  你…怎么突然弄成这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少…少主…不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了吧  刚才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是班长红
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的活跃度可真是超越预期呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  多亏了泉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的文化祭一定会很成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.95,0:16:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是说那种悠闲话的场合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  那不是小凪  她是被什么东西给附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然被看出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是把这个小女孩的负面感情化为力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而复活的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨灵！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…很完美的登场解说词  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把大小姐的身体还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小女孩和我很像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我生前也…也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去海边和游泳池游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  一直以来因为幼儿体形感到自卑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.49,0:17:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没穿过一次泳衣就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好恨  好恨！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨那些卖弄身体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来取悦男人们的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨那些一边喊着难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边暗自开心的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.24,0:18:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨那些不理解动画制作的难处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动不动就晃动胸部的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份恨意  不觉得应当发泄出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是个没气量的怨灵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…或者说  完全是在曲解别人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小女孩也和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充斥着被朋友排斥而产生的怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这家伙  比预料中要难对付呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  终于轮到我出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于等到我出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:49.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（EVA初号机登场！看样子凪家是第三新东京市。克劳斯身后应该加条电线才对）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧  保镖部队和警卫机器人们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去救出大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们敢对主人下手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.82,0:19:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好卑鄙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  戏份也到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  就让我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背后的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打倒操纵小凪的那个影子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏菊小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好高…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有恐高症  还硬要逞强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样才像雏菊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  这种时候就应该拜托伊澄…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…咋就偏偏不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂啊…漂啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都到哪里去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  伊澄又和往常一样地习惯性迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是传说中的「剧情需要」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…真是的  又迷路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无计可施了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐就由我来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区一个管家能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:48.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（实体剑突破GN-Field！）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  请回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐  请您抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微闹过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凪…飒先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然已经被各种动漫和游戏用到快烂掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是依然王道的  人工呼吸桥段？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不行  没时间犹豫了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.16,0:22:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去小飒会…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.30,0:22:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.25,0:22:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒你个大白痴！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.99,0:22:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪儿来的台词啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:22:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子是个无人岛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.88,0:23:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我很擅长野外求生的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.43,0:23:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在搜索队到来之前  我不会让大小姐吃苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.20,0:23:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.47,0:23:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.59,0:23:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我…如果我能再坦率一点的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.93,0:23:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.97,0:23:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  大小姐的泳衣很合身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨蛋  都这种时候了还说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.96,0:23:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也对呢  不过请不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.27,0:23:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算回不了宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会永远保护大小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.64,0:23:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我不介意的  只要有你在就行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.41,0:23:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是不是来得太早了点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.27,0:24:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.15,0:24:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  两个人都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.16,0:24:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连大家也…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.29,0:24:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.29,0:24:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里也算是在宅邸内
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.18,0:24:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.69,0:24:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦——？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.42,0:24:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒再一次体会到了三千院家财力的庞大
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.94,0:24:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方居然有海水浴场
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.69,0:24:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏露娜  就算是印度人也会吓一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.75,0:24:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文  我可一点都不吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.92,0:24:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道夏露娜是从外星来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.69,0:24:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文  请不要想到什么就马上说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.98,0:25:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,500日元～
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.33,0:25:06.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（入场费  500日元）
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.25,0:25:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾～
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.81,0:25:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿着这条路直走就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.22,0:25:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.81,0:25:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.73,0:25:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么  能解释一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.51,0:25:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  雏  这个月的生活费有点吃紧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.83,0:25:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.28,0:25:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算哪门子的解释
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.12,0:25:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把钱还回去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.49,0:25:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.93,0:25:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么姐姐你总是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------------------------------------------
